'''''Wako''''', ni Sinema ya [[Uganda]] yasohotse 2015 iyobowe na Zziwa Aaron Alone kandi yafatanije n’umuyobozi ubwe hamwe na Natuhwera Brighton na Wamasebu Eric kuri Zaron Motion Pictures, Brina Motion Pictures na Punchside Filmz<ref>http://artmatters.info/2015/11/situational-ethics-film-premieres-in-kampala/wako-film-by-aaron-alone-zziwa/</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201510071228.html</ref>. Nibisobanuro bya firime yambere  ''Hadithi za Kumekucha: TUNU'' .  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Geoffrey Echakara mu mwanya wa mbere mu kuyobora hamwe na Natuhwera Brighton, Robert Ernest Bbumba na Zziwa Aaron Alone mu nshingano zabo<ref>http://www.sunrise.ug/life-style/201611/zziwa-strikes-back-with-jobless-millionaires.html</ref>.<ref>https://samuelsaviour.wordpress.com/2015/10/03/award-winning-long-waited-ugandan-movie-wako-finally-premieres/</ref>  

Iyi filime yafashwe amashusho hagati ya 2014 kugeza hagati ya 2015 mucyaro no mu mijyi ya Kampala.  Iyi filime ivuga ku nkuru y’umugizi wa nabi w’igitsina gabo w’imyaka 23 witwa Wako wavuye muri gereza akabahambiriye gutangira ubuzima bushya, ariko yaje kumenya ko mushiki we arwaye kanseri<ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/magazine/uganda-awards-2016-best-films--1354754</ref>.<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Wako_(film)</ref> 

firime yagiye ahagaragara binyuze ku mbuga nkoranyambaga. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 1 Ukwakira 2016 muri Theatre La'bonita. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Muri 2015, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime nziza cyane mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime rya Arusha muri [[Tanzaniya]]<ref>https://www.filmcontact.com/africa/uganda/zziwa-shooting-ugandan-film-global-scene</ref>.<ref>https://samuelsaviour.wordpress.com/2015/11/11/award-winning-ugandan-gangster-movie-wako-on-for-a-country-tour/</ref>

